Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.81,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The Kamisato Clan's future, the duties of the Yashiro Commission...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:10.61,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,My brother should not bear these burdens alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:25.62,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,This belief is what has led me to this duel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:31.73,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"Check"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.55,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,When the Tsubaki is in season
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.14,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,I always have the same dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.94,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,My mother is with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.76,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,And I am at peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.04,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Maybe, somewhere deep down inside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:01:01.68,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The carefree days of family time have not ended for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.52,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,But just as flowers wither
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.90,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,I too must awaken from my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.05,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The Kamisato Art of Tachi Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:34.99,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Still like the morning dew, swift like lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:45.55,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Something stirs within me, perhaps the echo of a fond dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:50.35,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,But there it stays, day after day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.87,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Pushing me to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.46,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,And tempering my blade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:18.19,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I bested Brother in a duel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:28.64,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,It was also the moment that the Shirasagi Himegimi was born
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.95,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,It's show time, Ayaka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.75,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,The fireworks have started, everyone's waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:48.19,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,It was your wish to take over this side of things, if I recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.99,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Heh, sorry, Ayato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.87,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,We pray to our god:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:04.02,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,May all our dreams endure forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.33,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Narukami Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.74,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Let the festival begin!
